Package pt.iscte.es2.dto

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    FileUpload
    DTO FileUpload Contains the id of the persisted file uploaded, sessionId of the user that send the Jar Problem (File) and the filePath of where the file is located.
    OptimizationConfiguration
    DTO of OptimizationConfiguration Contains the following: problemName - Just a simple problem name description - Description of what the problem consists email - Email of the user that is submitting the OptimizationConfiguration filePath - Path of where the file is saved variablesQuantity - Number of Variables objectivesQuantity - Number of Objectives restrictionsQuantity - Number of Restrictions algorithmsQuantity - Number of Algorithms executionMaxWaitTime - Time to wait for the executions to run, in Seconds variables - List of OptimizationConfigurationVariables objectives - List of OptimizationConfigurationObjectives algorithms - List of OptimizationConfigurationAlgorithms restrictions - List of OptimizationConfigurationRestrictions userSolutions - List of OptimizationConfigurationUserSolutions executions - List of OptimizationJobExecutions algorithmChoiceMethod - AlgorithmChoiceMethod
    OptimizationConfigurationAlgorithms
    DTO of OptimizationConfigurationAlgorithms Contains the name of the Algorithm
    OptimizationConfigurationObjectives
    DTO of OptimizationConfigurationObjectives Contains the name of the Objective
    OptimizationConfigurationRestrictions
    DTO of OptimizationConfigurationRestrictions Contains the name of the Restrictions
    OptimizationConfigurationUserSolutions
    DTO of OptimizationConfigurationUserSolutions Contains the solution quality of the User
    OptimizationConfigurationVariables
    DTO of OptimizationConfigurationVariables Contains the name of the Variable
    OptimizationJobExecutions
    DTO of OptimizationJobExecutions Execution DTO that contains the id, startDate, endDate, state and possibly a list of solutions OptimizationJobSolutions
    OptimizationJobExecutionSummary
    DTO of OptimizationJobExecutionSummary Consists of a Summary that contains an executionId, optimizationConfigurationId, problemName, startDate, endDate and state of the Execution
    OptimizationJobSolutions
    DTO of OptimizationJobSolutions Contains the solutions generated by JMetal Framework of a certain Problem.
    SummaryOptimizationConfiguration
    DTO of SummaryOptimizationConfiguration Contains a Summary of an OptimizationConfiguration
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    AlgorithmChoiceMethod
    AlgorithmChoiceMethod DTO Enum that contains various options for the user to choose the Algorithms.
    State
    DTO of State Represents the state of an OptimizationJobExecutions
